  "texts": [
    "Only tweets written in English containing drug names from the top 500 prescribed medications in the US were included.",
    "Retweets and non-original content were excluded.",
    "Inter-annotator agreement for the categorization task was calculated using Fleiss' kappa and found to be 0.82, indicating good reliability between raters.",
    "Any tweets with discrepant labels were adjudicated through group discussion until consensus was reached.",
    "Of the total 23,516 tweets collected, 8289 (35.2%) were labeled as ADR and 15,227 (64.8%) as NON-ADR."
  ],
